Description:
You arrive at some strange circular ruins, in the center you can see a magic circle and around it you see twelve plates. Each plate has a rune and a different colored gem set in the center.

You inspect the runes carefully and see that when you press on them, the gem lights up and goes out after a while.

Upon further investigation, you realize that some of the runes are missing the gem and do not work, you also discover that you can make a combination of three runes before the gems go out.
DescriptionAction: It seems dangerous to try more random combinations...
